get.summary: Comprehensive data download to support Robust Review processes

Returns a time series representing pumped volume at a well or series of wells, summed daily for a given date range.
Each point in the output time series represents the total pumped volume for the given day.
get.description:
Sample requests:
            
    Returns data for ALL wells from 8/1/2021 to 8/31/2021
    GET /api/wells/pumpedVolume?startDate=2021-08-01&endDate=2021-08-31
            
    Returns data for Well Registration IDs G-056157, G-097457, G-110920 from 8/1/2021 to 8/31/2021
    GET /api/wells/pumpedVolume?startDate=2021-08-01&endDate=2021-08-31&wellRegistrationID=G-056157&wellRegistrationID=G-097457&wellRegistrationID=G-110920

parameters.name: wellRegistrationID
parameters.description: The Well Registration ID(s) for the requested Well(s). If left blank, will bring back data for every Well that has reported data within the time range.

parameters.name: startDate
parameters.description: The start date for the report in yyyy-MM-dd format (eg. 2020-06-23)

parameters.name: endDate
parameters.description: The end date for the report in yyyy-MM-dd format (eg. 2020-06-23)
